        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_smoothsnake.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 486c204d-773b-4103-b4f4-829a3d944161).Image",
        "Description": "Hello, 47. Why not take a break to stop and smell the roses?\r\rYou&apos;re heading back to Thornbridge Manor today for the Dartmoor Garden Show. You have a total of five targets today: judge Sebastian Sato, guard Brok Tobin, and guests Kendra Jeanes, Charlie Randal, and Roxanne Winship. Client wants all targets killed in accidents... except Winship, curiously. In fact, they mention wanting her death to particularly painful. Maybe look around for ideas.\r\rHave a nice day, 47. Do try to enjoy yourself.",
